raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Babe wake up!
Player: You say that as if I'm asleep 😂
Mabel: Good morning 🤭
Mabel: Its such a nice and sunny day
Mabel: img: mabel/36
Mabel: What are you doing?
Player: I just finished my first class!
do social_post(\"valerie_intro\")
Mabel: Thought: I guess I was the lazy potato today then omg
Mabel: I still gotta get dressed
- What are you going to wear? 👀
	Player: What are you going to wear? 👀
	Mabel: Nothing special 😆
	Mabel: What do you think??
	- Something cute? [#love]
		set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
		Player: Something cute?
		Mabel: Yeah
		Mabel: Sometimes I feel like you're only with me for the cute pictures 🤭
		- Maybe. [#distrust]
			set Story.mabel_trust -= 1
			Player: Maybe.
			Mabel: Hey I was just kidding 😓
			Player: Am I not allowed to joke about it too 😅
			Mabel: You know it's not the same kind of joke 😠 Hmph 🥺
		- I'm with you because I love you [#love]
			set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
			Player: I'm with you because I love you
			Mabel: 🥰
			Mabel: No.
			Mabel: No way!
			Mabel: You can't be doing this to me while I'm in the middle of rushing 🥺🩷
			Player: Do what??
			Mabel: Torture me 😭
			Mabel: Now it's all I'll be thinking about omg
			Mabel: PinkThought: I seriously love you too!!!!!
	- Something sexy! [#lust]
		set Story.mabel_desire += 1
		Player: Something sexy!
		Mabel: No! Nope! I'm taking a little break from that haha
		Player: Awwh
		Mabel: Thought: If it was just for you, I would
		Mabel: I just don't...
		Mabel: I mean my legs were like totally BARE!!
		Mabel: People kept looking at them 😅
		Mabel: Thought: Maybe my butt too...
		- That's the whole point 🤤 [#distrust]
			set Story.mabel_desire += 1
			Player: That's the whole point 🤤
			Mabel: ??
			Mabel: Is that friend of yours giving you weird ideas??
			Mabel: 😳
		- I want to see that side of you 🔥 [#lust]
			set Story.mabel_desire += 1
			Player: I want to see that side of you 🔥
			Mabel: Wha- what do you mean??
			Mabel: I'm uhh.. I mean 😳
			Mabel: Thought: But... Do I even have a side like that?
	Mabel: Ok finished changing
	Mabel: Tadaa
	if Story.mabel_desire > 6:
		Mabel: img: mabel/38
		Mabel: Thought: This seems like a popular pose on Social
	else:
		Mabel: img: mabel/37
	Mabel: Next time I'll let you suggest what I should wear
	Mabel: Should be fun!
	Player: 😍
- What class is it?
	Player: What class is it?
	Mabel: It's called The History of Literature 🖼️
	Mabel: Pretty tough apparently, so much to memorize and learn! 😅
	Player: Good luck!
	Mabel: Thanks 🥰
	Mabel: What class did you have?
	Player: Calculus!
	Mabel: Oh that's a Math class right? Nerd! 🤓
	Mabel: How was it? Were you the smartest?
	Player: It was alright! It's tough 😅
	Mabel: It's okay! I believe in you 😘
	Mabel: Did you make any new friends there? What were the students like?
	- Nothing special 🙂
		Player: Nothing special 🙂
		Player: The usual crowds
		Mabel: If you say so 😘
	- A few scary jocks in my class 😅
		Player: A few jocks in my class 😅
		Mabel: Scary \"jocks\"? What's that?
		Player: They're like... muscly strong guys on the football team 🙃
		Mabel: O-oh! That sounds scary 😖
		Mabel: Will you be alright?
		- You'll have to protect me! 😘 [#love]
			set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
			Player: You'll have to protect me!
			Mabel: Of course silly 🥰
			Mabel: They better stay away from my boyfriend or they'll get a talking to!
			Mabel: img: mabel/39
			Player: Whoa scary!
			Mabel: That's my angry agent side 😇
		- I just have to keep my head down [#distrust]
			set Story.mabel_trust -= 1
			Player: I just have to keep my head down
			Mabel: Oh well okay
			Mabel: I don't want you getting hurt or anything babe
			Mabel: Please be careful and don't pick fights 🥺
			Player: I won't
Mabel: Oki dokes! I'm headed to class
Mabel: I'm so nervous omg
- I believe in you! [#love]
	set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
	Player: I believe in you!
	Mabel: Thanks babe!
	Mabel: I'll tell you all about it in the evening hehe
	Player: Can't wait!
- You'll be fine
	Player: You'll be fine
	Mabel: I hope so 😊
Mabel: Ttyl!
do social_post(\"naomi_hot\")
Player: Cya!
do social_post(\"mabel_studyroom\")
do social_post(\"erika_classslip\")
=> END"
